{
  "texts": [
    "The next day, transfection medium was removed and replaced with 18 mL fresh complete medium.",
    "Virus-containing cell culture medium was collected 24 h later.",
    "Cells were given another 18 mL of fresh medium and the virus was collected again 48 h posttransfection.",
    "Virus-containing medium was filtered through a 0.45 µm filter, then aliquoted and stored at -80 °C.",
    "CRISPR-Cas9 screens with DDR CRISPR library."
  ]
}